{{Flavour|Randomly translocates a targeted enemy a short distance. It cannot be resisted by willpower.}}

'''Blink Other''' is a monster-only spell which forces the target to [[blink]], ignoring the victim's [[willpower]]. If you are a [[Formicid]] or in [[Tree Form]], you will negate the effect, but it is otherwise irresistible.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.13]], Blink Other could also be negated if the spell failed to beat the target's magic resistance.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
